meal, and I left early.

189
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:27,070
This is just a token
of my apology...

190
00:12:27,610 --> 00:12:29,540
You didn't have
to do that...

191
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,650
I love "tsukudani".
(food boiled down in soy sauce)

192
00:12:34,180 --> 00:12:35,480
Thank you.

193
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,820
I'd better be going.

194
00:12:37,590 --> 00:12:39,290
Aren't you going
to come in?

195
00:12:39,290 --> 00:12:41,220
I just came by
to apologize...

196
00:12:42,020 --> 00:12:43,920
We didn't get to do
anything for you...

197
00:12:44,490 --> 00:12:45,490
I'll be going.

198
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:49,000
I'll see her off.

199
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,870
Thank you.

200
00:12:58,410 --> 00:12:59,740
Be careful!

201
00:13:04,180 --> 00:13:05,350
Yuka!

202
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:09,820
Don't tell me you came
here just to apologize?

203
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:20,630
I don't like your dancing,
but I like your house,

204
00:13:20,630 --> 00:13:24,460
and this town.

205
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,500
See you!

206
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:33,170
Thank you!

207
00:13:34,210 --> 00:13:36,210
I'll see you in school.

208
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:46,320
Hitomi felt like she had gotten
a little closer to Yuka.

209
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,940
Excuse me...

210
00:14:12,010 --> 00:14:14,280
Did you want something
at your house?

211
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,050
No... it's nothing.

212
00:14:25,830 --> 00:14:27,590
Who in the world
was that anyway?

